SwiftGUDHIFull — licensing
==========================

The original Swift source in this package is authored by Hiroaki Yamane (mnmly)
and offered under the MIT License (below).

HOWEVER, this package links `GudhiCoreFull.xcframework`, which statically links
CGAL packages licensed GPL-3.0-or-later (the dD triangulation behind the Alpha,
Tangential and Euclidean Witness modules) plus GMP/MPFR (LGPL-3.0). Therefore the
usable package, and any application that links it, is governed by
**GPL-3.0-or-later** (see LICENSE.GPL-3.0): such an application must itself be
GPL-3.0-compatible with its complete source available, and cannot be shipped
closed-source / on the App Store.

For a permissive (MIT/BSD) build without the CGAL modules, use the `SwiftGUDHI`
package on the `main` branch instead.

See THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md for the component inventory.

